create record

Usage:
  doctl compute domain records create <domain> [flags]

Aliases:
  create, c

Flags:
      --format string         Columns for output in a comma separated list. Possible values: ID,Type,Name,Data,Priority,Port,TTL,Weight
  -h, --help                  help for create
      --no-header             hide headers
      --record-data string    Record data
      --record-flags int      Record flags
      --record-name string    Record name
      --record-port int       Record port
      --record-priority int   Record priority
      --record-tag string     Record tag
      --record-ttl int        Record TTL (default 1800)
      --record-type string    Record type
      --record-weight int     Record weight

Global Flags:
  -t, --access-token string   API V2 Access Token
  -u, --api-url string        Override default API V2 endpoint
  -c, --config string         config file (default "/root/.config/doctl/config.yaml")
      --context string        authentication context
  -o, --output string         output format [text|json] (default "text")
      --trace                 trace api access
  -v, --verbose               verbose output